===[[Etymology]]===

L. ''[[accubatio]]'', for ''[[accubitio]]'', fr. ''[[accubare]]'' to [[recline]]; ''ad'' + ''[[cubare]]'' to lie down. See [[Accumb]].
===[[Noun]]===

The act or [[posture]] of [[reclining]] on a [[couch]], as [[practiced]] by the ancients at meals.
